Code.CodeDescription: WARNING – California Proposition 65 carcinogenic, teratogenic or other reproductively harmful chemical hazard
Code.CodeNotes: Required on applicable products sold in California. Must be accompanied in <ProductFormFeatureDescription> by specific additional text as displayed on product or packaging. For example, “WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals including [chemical name], which is known to the State of California to cause cancer. For more information, go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov”. Note long-form warnings should be used here, even if a short form warning is used on the product or packaging
